      "text": "<strong>Artist&rsquo;s signature</strong>: Hebrew initials of Ido Michaeli&rsquo;s name<br /><br />The signature for&nbsp;Yitzhak Mattat<span>&rsquo;s carpet shop&nbsp;was&nbsp;distorted in production.</span>"
