      "text": "<p><img src=\"images/058a.jpg\" alt=\"Baron (Edmond Benjamin James) de Rothschild, Zionist philanthropist  and member of a Jewish banking dynasty\" width=\"400\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Baron (Edmond Benjamin James) de Rothschild</strong>, Zionist philanthropist and member of a Jewish banking dynasty</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"images/058b.jpg\" alt=\"Karl Marx, revolutionary thinker of Jewish origin whose work introduced a new understanding of economic power relations at work in society  \" width=\"400\" height=\"584\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Karl Marx</strong>, revolutionary thinker of Jewish origin whose work introduced a new understanding of economic power relations at work in society &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p></p>"
