      "text": "<p><img src=\"images/074.jpg\" alt=\"Heinrich B&uuml;nting, Clover-leaf map of the world with Jerusalem at the center, first published 1581\" width=\"400\" height=\"316\" /></p>\r\n<p>Heinrich B&uuml;nting, <strong>Clover-leaf map of the world with Jerusalem at the center</strong>, first published 1581</p>\r\n<p></p>"
